Oh, and after one, the sun is going to shine.

00:15.277 --> 00:19.945
Oh, and after one, the dark clouds will all pass over.

00:19.985 --> 00:27.658
We will shout hallelujah after one.

00:28.904 --> 00:57.088
There's a leaf, the eye is always watching Oh, trying to see everything that you do Oh, there's a leaf, the tongue is always busy It will lie on me and lie on you Oh, but after a while

00:57.541 --> 00:59.944
It all will be over.

01:02.106 --> 01:06.451
Oh, after a while, the sun is going to shine.

